title: YoGeeDaDee Organic Lifestyle
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Taiwanese
description: Small organic shop and kitchen operating since 2005. Offers vegetarian food for breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Has a few tables in the back for seating. Shop stocks a range of packaged dried food stuff including seaweed, crackers, grains, dried fruit, and others. There is a refrigerated food section in the back.
